270
00:15:22,774 --> 00:15:26,855
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">The stars have aligned to open the path to quintessence.</font>

271
00:15:26,856 --> 00:15:29,713
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">The Great Cathedral will house the rite,</font>

272
00:15:29,714 --> 00:15:32,571
