273
00:15:32,572 --> 00:15:36,245
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">Fate has it that you will all arrive tomorrow,</font>

274
00:15:36,246 --> 00:15:38,694
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">For the day is our destiny:</font>

275
00:15:38,695 --> 00:15:40,735
