276
00:15:40,736 --> 00:15:43,593
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">We all must choose to embrace it.</font>

277
00:15:51,971 --> 00:15:54,000
<font color="#954444">(There are no further records.)</font>

278
00:15:58,001 --> 00:16:00,041
<font color="#954444">To whom it may concern,</font>

279
00:16:00,042 --> 00:16:04,531
<font color="#954444">We have heard some Brothers express doubt during the last Sabbath.</font>

280
00:16:04,532 --> 00:16:07,389
<font color="#954444">Hearing this fills me with profound sadness.</font>

281
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:11,471
<font color="#954444">But, while it goes without saying, remember your Masters' teachings.</font>

282
00:16:11,472 --> 00:16:17,186
<font color="#954444">Surely, you are aware of the consequences of denouncing the League in this manner.</font>

283
00:16:19,608 --> 00:16:23,281
<font color="#954444">For aeons, we have upheld tradition, awaiting this moment.</font>

284
00:16:23,282 --> 00:16:28,179
<font color="#954444">Thousands of our ancestors did not live to see this glorious day,</font>

285
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:31,445
<font color="#954444">but our patience has been rewarded at last.</font>

286
00:16:31,446 --> 00:16:36,343
<font color="#954444">We shall welcome the herald of a new era in twenty-seven days.</font>

287
00:16:36,344 --> 00:16:40,017
<font color="#954444">I must emphasize the importance of upholding tradition henceforth.</font>

288
00:16:40,018 --> 00:16:43,691
<font color="#954444">Only by following the past can we guarantee success.</font>

289
00:16:46,113 --> 00:16:51,419
