<font color="#d4d4d4">...is a monster.</font>

371
00:19:35,770 --> 00:19:37,388
<font class="speaker2" color="#33339f">Please Proceed.</font>

372
00:19:37,389 --> 00:19:39,000
<font class="speaker2" color="#33339f">Lest You Become Like Them.</font>

373
00:19:43,001 --> 00:19:45,858
<font color="#33339f">Those Who Disrespect Us Must Be Eradicated.</font>

374
00:19:45,859 --> 00:19:47,899
<font color="#33339f">We Are Order, Sense, Harmony.</font>

375
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:52,389
<font color="#33339f">The Eye Created Order In Form, And They Called It Space.</font>

376
00:19:52,390 --> 00:19:56,879
<font color="#33339f">The Eye Created Order In Flow, And They Called It Time.</font>

377
00:19:56,880 --> 00:20:00,145
<font color="#33339f">Without Our Laws, Everything Will Revert To Chaos.</font>

378
00:20:00,146 --> 00:20:03,003
<font color="#33339f">Without These Lands, Existence Loses All Value.</font>

379
00:20:03,004 --> 00:20:05,044
<font color="#33339f">But They Defy Us.</font>

380
00:20:05,045 --> 00:20:07,085
<font color="#33339f">But They Desire The Opposite.</font>

381
00:20:07,086 --> 00:20:10,351
<font color="#33339f">They Don't See The Beauty Of Our Laws.</font>

382
00:20:10,352 --> 00:20:12,800
<font color="#33339f">They Consider These Laws "Shackles" Instead.</font>

383
00:20:12,801 --> 00:20:15,658
<font color="#33339f">Their Chaos Is Seeping Into These Lands.</font>

384
00:20:15,659 --> 00:20:18,516
<font color="#33339f">Their Continuous Assaults Are Eroding These Lands.</font>

385
00:20:18,517 --> 00:20:21,374
<font color="#33339f">If These Lands Get Reduced To Naught,</font>

386
00:20:21,375 --> 00:20:26,272
<font color="#33339f">If The Pillars On Which The Laws Are Written Are But Rubble,</font>

387
00:20:26,273 --> 00:20:29,130
<font color="#33339f">The Cosmos Will Suffer Everywhere And Alltime.</font>

388
00:20:30,947 --> 00:20:35,028
<font color="#33339f">And While Unfortunate, We Have Become Unable To Stop Them.</font>

389
00:20:35,029 --> 00:20:38,294
<font color="#33339f">The Foot Has Already Been All But Destroyed.</font>

390
00:20:38,295 --> 00:20:40,743
<font color="#33339f">Nothing But An Indistinct Mist Remains.</font>

391
00:20:40,744 --> 00:20:43,601
<font color="#33339f">The Peak Won't Survive For Much Longer.</font>

392
00:20:43,602 --> 00:20:46,459
<font color="#33339f">Nothing We Do Seems To Affect Them.</font>

393
00:20:46,460 --> 00:20:49,317
<font color="#33339f">Their Final Assault Is Already In Motion.</font>

394
00:20:49,318 --> 00:20:51,358
<font color="#33339f">You. We Need You.</font>

395
00:20:51,359 --> 00:20:55,440
<font color="#33339f">You Cannot See It From Here, But See The Surface.</font>

396
00:20:55,441 --> 00:20:58,298
<font color="#33339f">A Land Without Form, Distorted By Impression.</font>

397
00:20:58,299 --> 00:21:01,156
<font color="#33339f">A Land Without Flow, Distorted By Emotion.</font>

398
00:21:01,157 --> 00:21:04,014
<font color="#33339f">An Unnavigable Realm Shaped By Vague Concepts.</font>

399
00:21:04,015 --> 00:21:08,912
<font color="#33339f">And They Want To Rid It Of Its Last Bastions Of Order.</font>

400
00:21:08,913 --> 00:21:11,361
<font color="#33339f">I Hope You Understand Our Plight.</font>

401
00:21:11,362 --> 00:21:13,402
<font color="#33339f">We Must Uphold Our Laws.</font>

402
00:21:15,219 --> 00:21:17,259
<font color="#33339f">But You...</font>

403
00:21:17,260 --> 00:21:19,708
<font color="#33339f">Why Even Visit These Barren Wastes?</font>

404
00:21:19,709 --> 00:21:22,566
<font color="#33339f">There Is Nothing To Be Gained Here.</font>

405
00:21:22,567 --> 00:21:24,607
<font color="#33339f">There Is But Wasted Time.</font>

406
00:21:24,608 --> 00:21:26,648
<font color="#33339f">Exert Your Efforts Elsewhere.</font>

407
00:21:26,649 --> 00:21:31,138
<font color="#33339f">We Do Not See The Need For You To Visit Here.</font>

408
00:21:31,139 --> 00:21:33,587
<font color="#33339f">For You Will Not Remember Here.</font>

409
00:21:33,588 --> 00:21:37,261
<font color="#33339f">Do You See Those Rock Formations To Your Right?</font>

410
00:21:37,262 --> 00:21:40,119
<font color="#33339f">Do You See The Buildings On Top?</font>

411
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:42,160
<font color="#33339f">You Shall Go There Instead.</font>

412
00:21:42,161 --> 00:21:45,000
<font color="#33339f">You Shall Help Our Fight There Instead.</font>

413
00:21:49,001 --> 00:21:51,041
<font color="#467546">Phew.</font>

414
00:21:51,042 --> 00:21:53,082
<font color="#467546">This stupid place.</font>

415
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:56,756
<font color="#467546">Ever since I fell, everything has been so hectic.</font>

416
00:21:56,757 --> 00:22:00,022
<font color="#467546">That stupid Eye should've just given me wings!</font>

417
00:22:00,023 --> 00:22:03,696
<font color="#467546">The only reason I'm still alive is pure luck.</font>

418
00:22:03,697 --> 00:22:07,370
<font color="#467546">Come on, no one could survive such a fall!</font>

419
00:22:07,371 --> 00:22:13,085
<font color="#467546">But the trees caught me, I only had a few bruises, and that's that.</font>

420
00:22:17,201 --> 00:22:20,058
<font color="#467546">I'm glad I've found this little area.</font>

421
00:22:20,059 --> 00:22:23,732
<font color="#467546">The endless supply of water flowing through these gorges...</font>

422
00:22:23,733 --> 00:22:27,406
<font color="#467546">The gentle breeze between the cliffs swaying the vines...</font>

423
00:22:27,407 --> 00:22:29,447
<font color="#467546">I can actually... relax here.</font>

424
00:22:29,448 --> 00:22:33,121
<font color="#467546">I know I shouldn't let my guard down though.</font>

425
00:22:33,122 --> 00:22:36,387
<font color="#467546">With all the beasts up there and whatnot.</font>

426
00:22:36,388 --> 00:22:39,245
<font color="#467546">Not to mention the Eye's incessant demands.</font>

427
00:22:39,246 --> 00:22:42,511
<font color="#467546">But here, I can finally take a breather...</font>

428
00:22:46,627 --> 00:22:49,075
<font color="#467546">Still, it really messes with me.</font>

429
00:22:49,076 --> 00:22:51,933
<font color="#467546">Who am I? What is this place?</font>

430
00:22:51,934 --> 00:22:56,423
<font color="#467546">This sky has no sun... but it feels like it should.</font>

431
00:22:56,424 --> 00:22:59,689
<font color="#467546">There is just no sense of time here.</font>

432
00:22:59,690 --> 00:23:04,179
<font color="#467546">And having to be on my guard, always, is so taxing.</font>

433
00:23:04,180 --> 00:23:09,077
<font color="#467546">But in these ravines, I can hardly see the sky at all.</font>

434
00:23:09,078 --> 00:23:11,935
<font color="#467546">Without that eerie twilight in my view...</font>

435
00:23:11,936 --> 00:23:14,384
<font color="#467546">Without the beasts that roam around...</font>

436
00:23:14,385 --> 00:23:16,425
<font color="#467546">Let's take a nap...</font>

437
00:23:20,541 --> 00:23:22,989
<font color="#467546">Why do I always forget dreams?</font>

438
00:23:22,990 --> 00:23:25,847
<font color="#467546">I feel like this one was important.</font>

439
00:23:25,848 --> 00:23:27,888
<font color="#467546">Funny how that works.</font>

440
00:23:27,889 --> 00:23:29,929
<font color="#467546">Well then. Well now.</font>

441
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:34,000
<font color="#467546">Let's see if I can Remember anything around these parts.</font>

442
00:23:38,001 --> 00:23:41,266
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">Venerable Lord Mettiyah, the Red Bell has rung.</font>

443
00:23:41,267 --> 00:23:44,124
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">Venerable Lord Mettiyah, the King has perished.</font>

444
00:23:44,125 --> 00:23:46,573
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">Venerable Lord Mettiyah, teach us Death.</font>

445
00:23:46,574 --> 00:23:49,022
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">Venerable Lord Mettiyah, teach us Birth.</font>

446
00:23:49,023 --> 00:23:53,512
<font color="#954444">Honored Brothers, it was set in the Stars, was it not?</font>

447
00:23:53,513 --> 00:23:58,002
<font color="#954444">That on this accursed Day, I were to teach you Death.</font>

448
00:23:58,003 --> 00:24:00,860
<font color="#954444">Soon, Honored Brothers, shall the Sky shatter;</font>

449
00:24:00,861 --> 00:24:03,718
<font color="#954444">Soon, Honored Brothers, shall the Water whiten;</font>

450
00:24:03,719 --> 00:24:07,392
<font color="#954444">And soon, Honored Brothers, shall Silence befall the Sanctuary.</font>

451
00:24:07,393 --> 00:24:09,841
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">We w█▓▒▒▓▒ ▓▓██▓█ (We w█▓▒▒▓▒ ▓▓██▓█)</font>

452
00:24:13,154 --> 00:24:15,194
<font color="#954444">Since all Things are Omnipresent,</font>

453
00:24:15,195 --> 00:24:17,643
<font color="#954444">cultivate the Perception of the Omnipresent.</font>

454
00:24:17,644 --> 00:24:20,092
<font color="#954444">You shall humbly accept the star-gourd.</font>

455
00:24:20,093 --> 00:24:22,133
<font class="speaker2" color="#954444">I ▓█▓▓▓██ ▓██▓▓ ▒▓▓▒▓██</font>

456
00:24:25,446 --> 00:24:27,894
<font color="#954444">Since They are possessed of Desire,</font>

457
00:24:27,895 --> 00:24:29,935
<font color="#954444">cultivate the Perception of Desire.</font>

458
00:24:29,936 --> 00:24:32,384
<font color="#954444">You shall humbly accept the blood-gourd.</font>

459
